  <summary date="2021-05-25T13:56:20Z" status="Introduced in Senate">COVID-19 Diaper Assistance Act

This bill provides additional funding for FY2021 for the Social Services Block Grant to provide diapers, wipes, and other diapering supplies to families in need. This grant is a flexible funding stream used by states and territories to support a wide range of social services.</summary>
